<% breadcrumb :demo_home %>

<div class="demo-section">
  <h2>Welcome to the Gretel Bulma Breadcrumbs Demo</h2>

  <div class="content">
    <p>
      This demo showcases all the different Bulma breadcrumb styles available in Gretel.
      Click on the buttons above to see each variation in action.
    </p>

    <h3>Available Demos:</h3>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Default</strong> - Basic Bulma breadcrumb style</li>
      <li><strong>Arrow</strong> - Breadcrumb with arrow separator (→)</li>
      <li><strong>Bullet</strong> - Breadcrumb with bullet separator (•)</li>
      <li><strong>Dot</strong> - Breadcrumb with dot separator (·)</li>
      <li><strong>Succeeds</strong> - Breadcrumb with succeeds separator (≻)</li>
      <li><strong>Small</strong> - Small size breadcrumb</li>
      <li><strong>Medium</strong> - Medium size breadcrumb</li>
      <li><strong>Large</strong> - Large size breadcrumb</li>
      <li><strong>Combined</strong> - Arrow separator with large size</li>
      <li><strong>With Parent</strong> - Breadcrumb with parent hierarchy</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <h3>Current Breadcrumb:</h3>
  <div class="result">
    <%= breadcrumbs style: :bulma %>
  </div>
</div>
